lead_paragraph: PARKER--David L.,92. United Methodist minister for 54 years. A life of faith, music, and love. Survived by three daughters, Julie Faith Parker (Bill Crawford), Kate Parker-Burgard (Don), and Valerie Parker, and six grandchildren, Graham, Mari, Jacob, Eli, Maxwell, and Josephine. Services and obituary: JJFFH.com 1/3
